Summary: I was watching the stars at the beach and saw 2 crafts
divs: Sighting DetailsI was star gazing and saw first one craft soundlessly hover and then move across sky. After a few minutes a second craft appeared at a lower altitude. Could have been the same craft appearing for the light was the same color and no sound with smooth and seamless motion across sky.
